Geek-Girl_000_(2012)_(Digital)_(DR_&_Quinch-Empire)


A PR co-ed at Acorn Ridge college, Maine: Ruby Kaye hangs with the in-crowd, is top of the party-invite list, and has guys queuing up. But EVERYTHING'S about to change for Ruby. GEEK-GIRL begins here!

Ruby is gonna find out just how flimsy her 'cool kid'-based friendships are; and by the end of Geek-Girl #0, she ain't gonna have many left. Oh, but that'll be the least of her problems, with who--or WHAT--then shows up!
